{"tid":2362411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺疫情已經KO哂班環保膠？","createTime":"2021-01-11T12:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T16:19:30.000Z","uid":57405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a87cd1ff5cc372e484963b04f6f5bfc0902234fa","tid":2362411,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:08:54.000Z","msg":"成年都唔知浪費左幾多口罩、紙巾、外賣盒&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5ccfddf60f7bc67cb8ba44a7a3f940b9782fb9","tid":2362411,"uid":266428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"留名等睇幾年後有海龜比口罩纏死<br />\n跟著d環保撚就開始出post批鬥全世界響疫情期間乜乜乜<br />\n再spin去即棄餐具碗碟，計畫通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d4bfa198b846756e93793497d633fa37c85308","tid":2362411,"uid":41352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:14:42.000Z","msg":"你講岩左<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-12-2021/69552?fbclid=IwAR3ie1qwOON1aHHYMWLzoOCdEJw8PWmmwVVGVq4hv53b3OcxtK4k0UyKot4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-12-2021%2F69552%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ie1qwOON1aHHYMWLzoOCdEJw8PWmmwVVGVq4hv53b3OcxtK4k0UyKot4&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=55824052\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-12-2021/69552?fbclid=IwAR3ie1qwOON1aHHYMWLzoOCdEJw8PWmmwVVGVq4hv53b3OcxtK4k0UyKot4</a><br />\n<br />\n防疫物資釀生態危機 巴西發現企鵝屍體胃內有口罩<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/202101/20210112mask.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F202101%2F20210112mask.jpg&h=a794ee4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去一年，人類大量使用口罩，並且沒有妥善處理，造成了生態危機，有動物更因此而喪命。 善待動物組織（PETA）人員接受《法新社》訪問時表示，口罩無法很快消失於自然環境，丟棄後會對環境與一同生活在地球的動物造成傷害。 根據環保團體「海洋亞洲」（OceansAsia）資料，去年有超過15億個口罩流入全球海洋，相當於新增6200噸海洋塑膠污染。 去年9月，巴西保育人士在被沖上岸的企鵝屍體的胃內，發現一個口罩，在邁阿密外海，也有河豚因口罩而喪命。法國的非營利組織「海洋清潔行動」（Operation Mer Propre）於去年9月，亦曾在地中海的鹹水潟湖，發現一隻困死於口罩裡的螃蟹。"},{"pid":"60c57854fc5a5d9a413a29074c3c52df3e5bef4b","tid":2362411,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29d4bfa198b846756e93793497d633fa37c85308","tid":2362411,"uid":41352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:14:42.000Z","msg":"你講岩左<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-12-2021/69552?fbclid=IwAR3ie1qwOON1aHHYMWLzoOCdEJw8PWmmwVVGVq4hv53b3OcxtK4k0UyKot4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-12-2021%2F69552%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ie1qwOON1aHHYMWLzoOCdEJw8PWmmwVVGVq4hv53b3OcxtK4k0UyKot4&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=55824052\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-12-2021/69552?fbclid=IwAR3ie1qwOON1aHHYMWLzoOCdEJw8PWmmwVVGVq4hv53b3OcxtK4k0UyKot4</a><br />\n<br />\n防疫物資釀生態危機 巴西發現企鵝屍體胃內有口罩<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/202101/20210112mask.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F202101%2F20210112mask.jpg&h=a794ee4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去一年，人類大量使用口罩，並且沒有妥善處理，造成了生態危機，有動物更因此而喪命。 善待動物組織（PETA）人員接受《法新社》訪問時表示，口罩無法很快消失於自然環境，丟棄後會對環境與一同生活在地球的動物造成傷害。 根據環保團體「海洋亞洲」（OceansAsia）資料，去年有超過15億個口罩流入全球海洋，相當於新增6200噸海洋塑膠污染。 去年9月，巴西保育人士在被沖上岸的企鵝屍體的胃內，發現一個口罩，在邁阿密外海，也有河豚因口罩而喪命。法國的非營利組織「海洋清潔行動」（Operation Mer Propre）於去年9月，亦曾在地中海的鹹水潟湖，發現一隻困死於口罩裡的螃蟹。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}